It‘s informative and easy to read even if its topics are completely unfamiliar to you. I had so much fun listening to the audiobook and I wish more books meant to popularize science were this accessible.

* Recommended if you like vlogbrothers’ Crash Course, SciShow and/or Emily Graslie’s The Brain Scoop;

* Large number of books mentioned can be used to compile a decent reading list if a particular chapter or a period strikes your fancy.
